original_title: Chikara: Young Lions Cup IV - Night Two
overview: Sixteen more wrestlers try their best to make it to the Young Lions Cup finals by winning a singles match, and then winning a 6-way elimination match! Ice Cream, Junior makes his CHIKARA debut, Shane Storm and Jigsaw team up to take on F.I.S.T, and Eddie Kingston has some words for the always-antagonistic Larry Sweeney!
title: Chikara: Young Lions Cup IV - Night Two
